items.name: R2-Auto-Bot-
items.description: This script automates USDC ↔ R2USD swaps and R2USD staking on Sepolia testnet 🚀. Features a hacker-style UI 🖥️, menu-driven interface, dynamic gas estimation ⛽, and multiple RPCs for reliability 🌐. Executes tasks sequentially, pauses 24 hours 🔄, and skips failed transactions with no emojis in logs ✅.
